<i>noun</i>: 수도자 [수도자], 수녀 [수녀] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>수도자 [수도자]</dt><br>
<dd>1. ascetic</dd><br>
<dd>도를 닦는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who cultivates himself/herself spiritually or religiously.</dd><br>
<dd>2. monk; nun</dd><br>
<dd>가톨릭에서, 수도사나 수녀.</dd><br>
<dd>A monk or nun in Catholicism.</dd><br>
<dt>수녀 [수녀]</dt><br>
<dd>nun; sister</dd><br>
<dd>가톨릭에서, 신에게 서약하고 독신으로 수도하는 여자.</dd><br>
<dd>An unmarried female who makes an oath to God and practices asceticism in Catholicism.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>